data.description: Gorgeous 3 Bdrm 2 1/2 bath home on corner lot with huge backyard.  Large open floor plan with beautiful floor tiles the entire main floor.  The large Master Bedroom with big walk-in closet has a Jetted bathtub in the Master Bath. Kitchen has tall spacious cabinets, large pantry and utility rm. The property has beautiful views all the way to downtown S.A.. I-35 Forum mall, Costco, EVO-entertainment and Schlitterbahn are all in close proximity. Come, relax and BBQ at the covered patio pad.  Close to all bases
